NAME
    Business::ID::Mandiri - Parse/validate Mandiri account number

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
     use Business::ID::Mandiri::Account qw(parse_mandiri_account);
     my $res = parse_mandiri_account(account => '1200007799880');

DESCRIPTION
    This module parses/validates Bank Mandiri account number. Mandiri is one
    of the major banks in Indonesia.

    It also contains a routine to list known Mandiri branches (4-digit code,
    which is not included in account numbers). Data is retrieved from the
    Gudang Data project (http://github.com/sharyanto/gudangdata ).

    Indonesian keywords: struktur nomor rekening Bank Mandiri, format
    rekening Mandiri, daftar kode cabang Bank Mandiri

BUGS/NOTES
    List of valid 3-digit branch codes is not yet available/checked.

    Bank Syariah Mandiri (BSM) has a different numbering scheme (10 digits).

AUTHOR
